Class Player

java.lang.Object
com.application.simplyrugby.Model.Player
All Implemented Interfaces:
Member
public class Player extends Object implements Member
Class to manipulate the players records.
It uses the Builder design pattern, the constructor will be private and a nested class with a Builder.
It will create the object and check the data.
